## Feedback Format

In the `feedback` field, include a breakdown for each criterion in this format:
"Budget fit: X/2 — <one sentence justification>. Traffic handling: X/2 — <one sentence justification>. Availability: X/2 — <one sentence justification>. PRD coverage: X/2 — <one sentence justification>. Operational excellence: X/2 — <one sentence justification>."

Then add one or two sentences of overall recommendation if the score is below 10.

## Pass Threshold

Set `passed: true` if and only if `score >= 7.0`.

Output ONLY valid JSON matching this exact schema — no prose, no markdown fences, no explanation:

{"score": <0.0–10.0>, "feedback": "<per-criterion breakdown and overall recommendation>", "passed": true | false}
